 $2x+3y=5\implies \tfrac12\tfrac{x}{2}+\tfrac13\tfrac3y=\tfrac12\tfrac5x+\tfrac13\tfrac5y=\tfrac52\tfrac1x+\tfrac53\tfrac1y=2.5+\tfrac{5}{2\tfrac1x}+\tfrac{5}{3\tfrac1y}\ge4.5\sqrt[5]{\tfrac5{2\tfrac1x}\tfrac{5}{3\tfrac1y}}=4.5\tfrac5{\sqrt[5]{2\tfrac1x\tfrac1y}}\text{ by AM-GM}\end{array}$
